title: Flight Sim World v1.3.22392.0
description: The future of flight simulation has arrived! Choose from our fleet of sleek, highly-detailed aircraft and take-off to exotic places through a variety of spectacular weather conditions. Take on one of our challenging missions, create your own flight plan, or climb the ranks with our authentic LAPL, PPL and Multi-Engine lessons. Flight Sim World includes: Seven gorgeous single and twin propeller aircraft Advanced weather engine powered by trueSKY technologyImmersive lessons and challenging
